                            <comment id="15953296" author="strelok1" created="Mon, 3 Apr 2017 11:14:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=serg.berezhnoy&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;serg.berezhnoy&quot;&gt;serg.berezhnoy&lt;/a&gt; thank you. 3.1.10 is used by latest camel-cxf and this was not working. I will raise an issue in Apache Camel project to update this dependency ASAP. &lt;/p&gt;

